name: @ionic-native/in-app-browser
readme: Improve this doc # In App Browser ``` $ ionic cordova plugin add cordova-plugin-inappbrowser $ npm install @ionic-native/in-app-browser@beta ``` ## [Usage Documentation](https://ionicframework.com/docs/native/in-app-browser/) Plugin Repo: [https://github.com/apache/cordova-plugin-inappbrowser](https://github.com/apache/cordova-plugin-inappbrowser) Launches in app Browser ## Supported platforms - AmazonFire OS - Android - Browser - iOS - macOS - Windows
